Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68632,72002}{\i1}The city of fog, London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:72002,76573}{\i1}After overcoming numerous dangers,\NIsabelle and Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76573,80644}{\i1}finally arrived\Nat their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81077,84114}Excuse me, do you know someone\Nnamed Martin Schmidt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84114,86016}Is Mr. Martin Schmidt here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86349,89085}Martin?\NCan't say it rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93256,95759}– What are you doing?\N– "What are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95759,99996}Ha. If you don't like the smoke of a cigar,\Nyou'd better get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99996,103633}This is not the place for such munchkins,\Nall wet behind their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103633,104701}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104701,106636}Oh, did I upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106636,111541}If you're such a man, why don't you take your\Npants off and show what you have under?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111541,113543}Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116513,118582}Come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118582,120383}We're all waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122185,123753}Give them a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125288,127924}One of you is Isabelle\Nand you have news from Paris, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127924,129893}Paris? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130694,132596}How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133063,137233}I've heard a bit about Jules from Paris.\NI will introduce you to Martin Schmidt.
